race.description: Download The Bet Nation App 5/6 Grade F
race.comment: NAVABI (2) is in hot form after clocking a handy 28.88 victory two back then followed up with a 28.69 win at this track over 498m last time. Clocking fast times and looks a key chance again here. ASTON KINNIE (1) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 4 last time (28.94) at this track. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Expected to feature. SWING SHIFT (4) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish a neck away in second (28.83) behind DON'T TELL SHILO at this track. Yet to taste defeat from two runs out of this box. Will give a great sight again. HIDDEN FURY (7) showed plenty of dash to record a last start win. Big chance on that form.
